  <graph edgedefault="undirected">
    <node id="Andrew Ng">
      <data key="d0">Andrew Ng</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Andrew Ng is the instructor for the Machine Learning course, providing guidance and announcements related to project proposals and course expectations.&lt;SEP&gt;Andrew Ng is the instructor explaining Newton’s Method and its application to logistic regression and other model-fitting techniques.&lt;SEP&gt;Andrew Ng is an instructor discussing algorithms in a learning environment, particularly focusing on Newton's Method and its application in logistic regression.&lt;SEP&gt;Andrew Ng is the instructor leading the lecture, providing explanations on statistical concepts and distributions.&lt;SEP&gt;Andrew Ng is an instructor involved in teaching topics related to likelihood and parameters in a statistical model.&lt;SEP&gt;Andrew Ng is an instructor discussing statistical models in a lecture, focusing on logistic regression and generalized linear models.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1dcfa4fdc2012c4e3a3c336e39e4afec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d9737bbcc99dd55bb4b79cf055977a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aa4c1f1bcccecc7faef4f12ad096763&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac0a1ea80eae7c222bf0ffd73875b023&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d65cfad802d1335db113217e2cb6afbe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-023cc775f8b1adeebc9c45d2e9f6fe90</data>
