      <data key="d0">Function F</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Function F is a mathematical expression dependent on theta, used to illustrate concepts in optimization and convergence in Newton’s Method.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7d9737bbcc99dd55bb4b79cf055977a2</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
