    <node id="Local Optimum">
      <data key="d0">Local Optimum</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The local optimum refers to a point in optimization where a function value is better than its neighboring values, which is essential in algorithms like Newton's Method.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7d9737bbcc99dd55bb4b79cf055977a2</data>
