      <data key="d0">Theta Superscript Zero</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Theta superscript zero represents the initial value of the parameter theta used in Newton’s Method and is critical for the iteration process.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7d9737bbcc99dd55bb4b79cf055977a2</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
