      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Probability distribution is a mathematical function that provides the probabilities of occurrence of different possible outcomes in an experiment.&lt;SEP&gt;Probability distribution describes how probabilities are distributed over the values of a random variable.</data>
